FBIS4-13988 "drnes080_v_94008" FBIS-NES-94-080 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 Pakistan PRC To Train 60 Chashma Nuclear Plant Operators PRC To Train 60 Chashma Nuclear Plant Operators BK2604132894 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network in English 1100 GMT 26 Apr 94 BK2604132894 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network English BFN [Text] Sixty operators of the Chashma Nuclear Power Plant have been inducted into a Chinese training school for basic training in safety measures and maintenance of the plant. Under a contract signed by the two countries, the Chinese Nuclear Corporation is to provide various technical facilities to Pakistani technicians for the smooth operation of the 300-megawatt plant.
